Working on this belief, we want to bring a metaverse to the IC. We’ve started with a collection of ICPunks and Infinity Frogs. Our next goal is to create a bridge from Ethereum to IC, so that people can freely move NFTs (also Decentraland assets) to the IC and back. The next step would be to establish a DAO to fuel the growth of the crosschain ecosystem of apps and tools. We believe in the open gasless NFT ecosystem.
